message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs and expectations. This exceptional item is valued at $120 by both myself and you, ensuring a perfect match for your requirements. Considering its high quality and utility, I am extending an exclusive offer to you at a special price of $110. Don't miss this opportunity to own a product that promises to exceed your satisfaction. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
